data.description: Here it is, this is arguably the most beautifully designed home in the Highly Desirable Cloppers Mill West subdivision.  It is certainly the most unique and among the largest boasting 6 bedrooms/5 full baths and truly gorgeous from the moment you cross the threshold. Awash in natural light, no need to even turn a light on.  The 2-story foyer with front and rear staircases and living room set the stage for comfortable family living and entertaining.  From the two private first floor bedrooms and huge first floor full bath with double vanity, to the open family room/eat-in kitchen, this home boasts space without feeling cavernous.  On the upper level, you will find the primary bedroom suite, complete with private bath and walk-in closet. 3 additional bedrooms and 2 full baths, as well as a family entertainment area/study space. A fully finished walk-out basement with a huge recreation area, bonus room/office, full bath & ample storage complete this wonderful home!  Enjoy entertaining on the oversized nearly wrap around deck. New carpet, fresh paint throughout, newer roof and systems - most systems still under warranty - this home is ready for its new owners and can accommodate nearly any living situation and needs.
